code: /**  * Specify if the cache entry should be remove before invoking the method. By default, the  * cache entry is removed after the method invocation.  * @see javax.cache.annotation.CacheRemove#afterInvocation()  */ public boolean isEarlyRemove() {     return !getCacheAnnotation().afterInvocation(). }
